      "content": "it just never stops. no matter what i do or what meds i take, the nerve pain is just... it's constant. i'm so tired of fighting just to get through a single hour. i feel like i'm just a body that's broken and everyone is just waiting for me to get better, but they don't get that there is no better. there's just more of this.",
