    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it just feels like i'm trapped in a loop. every day is just... a different version of the same misery. sometimes i sit here and i don't even see a future, just a long, dark hallway of more pain. it almost feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just stop everything. like, wouldn't it be more merciful to just let it end than to keep dragging this broken thing along?",
